        {
            "title": "花旗集團股價因潛在收購地區銀行報導下跌4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RRT_xg1M9RiRqWuUwZgKag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7H00D_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 花旗集團(NYSE:C)股價週五下跌4%,此前彭博社報導該銀行正考慮收購一家地區性銀行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博社報導,這家總部位於紐約的銀行高層近幾個月就收購一家地區性銀行以增加按金進行了初步討論,此舉可能支持其貸款和交易業務。一些高管在今年與美國監管機構的會議上提出了這種可能性,監管當局表示願意審查正式提案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span>花旗集團</span></span></span></span>目前仍受兩項同意令約束,在進行任何收購之前需要獲得監管機構批准。該銀行否認了這一報導,表示「有關花旗計劃收購地區性銀行、財富經紀公司或任何其他金融服務公司的說法純屬毫無根據的猜測。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-678a84e3-0e18-3d45-a6a4-bcd2acfb94f2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據報導,花旗集團可能瞄準資產約5000億美元的銀行,包括Truist Financial Corp.(NYSE:TFC)和PNC Financial Services Group Inc.(NYSE:PNC),這兩家銀行的市值均超過500億美元。該銀行還表示有興趣收購Stifel Financial Corp.(NYSE:SF)或Raymond James Financial Inc.(NYSE:RJF)等經紀公司。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博社報導引述的消息人士稱,討論仍處於早期階段,不能保證該公司會提出正式提議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
